The paper discusses the intersection of Big Data and IoT, which is a key area of research in the Internet of Things (cs.IOT) sub-category. The paper also discusses various methods and techniques that can be used in this area, including Machine Learning (cs.LG) and hardware developments (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper touches on the digital economy, which falls under the Database (cs.DB) and Software Engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
